<div class="postright">
<h3>Re: Bluetooth Connection before login</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>You need to boot live, and enable autologin under /etc/lightdm/*.conf of your root fs<br/>There is an autologin=user option to uncomment&#160; and put instead of user the username of the account</p>
</div>
<div class="postsignature postmsg"><hr/><p>-Jeff Szydel </p><p>*Parrot Ambassador&#160; &#160;*Social Groups Manager&#160; &#160;*Helpdesk&#160; &#160;*Wiki Editor&#160; &#160; <br/>*Parrot Telegram Group Administrator&#160; &#160;*Parrot Community Administrator</p></div>
